|3 |    └─EXCHANGE IN DISTR                   |        |
|4 |      └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (HASH)         |:EX10001|
|5 |        └─SHARED HASH JOIN                |        |
|6 |          ├─EXCHANGE IN DISTR             |        |
|7 |          │ └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (BC2HOST)|:EX10000|
|8 |          │   └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR         |        |
|9 |          │     └─TABLE FULL SCAN         |a       |
|10|          └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR             |        |
|11|            └─TABLE FULL SCAN             |b       |
========================================================
